### ============================================
### Authentication Endpoints
### ============================================

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Logout User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Current User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### ============================================
### Users Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get User List
GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/list?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### Get User By ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/USER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### Update Current User Profile
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/user/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

###

### ============================================
### Conversations Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get User Conversations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/conversations?page=1&limit=20
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### Create New Conversation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "participantIds": ["USER_ID_1", "USER_ID_2"],
  "type": "direct",
  "name": "Conversation Name"
}

###

### Get Conversation By ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### ============================================
### Messages Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get Conversation Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/messages/conversation/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE?page=1&limit=50
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### Mark Conversation Messages as Read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/messages/conversation/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE/read
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

